abstract: Officials in Panama City Beach, Fla, hold emergency City Council meeting to address issue of raucous spring break season after weekend house party ends in gunfire that injured at least seven young people.
lead_paragraph: Gunfire at a weekend house party in Panama City Beach, Fla., that left seven young people hurt has officials pondering what to do with a spring break season they say has gotten out of control.

headline.main: Panama City Beach Increases Spring Break Patrols
